snippet.title: HERE'S WHAT AMBER HEARD DID BEFORE BECOMING JOHNNY DEPP'S WIFE
snippet.description:
Source : http://www.zimbio.com/

Have you Heard? Amber had a successful acting career before meeting Johnny Depp on the set of The Rum Diaries. A product of modest Texas beginnings, the young actress fought tooth and nail for each role she portrayed, proving herself with every small, typecast job until she finally won rights to the big screen. Keep clicking to check out her past roles.
